OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Flargely cloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with further showery
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain, these will be heavy
OL,9,Fand thundery at times. Gentle winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FCloudier at first with heavy,
OL,12,Fshowery overnight rain soon clearing.
OL,13,FThen bright or sunny spells and
OL,14,Fscattered showers.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloud
OL,17,Fand outbreaks of rain soon spreading
OL,18,Feast on Monday. Cloudy on Tuesday with
OL,19,Foccasionally heavy rain or showers.
OL,20,FFurther showers or longer spells of
OL,21,Frain on Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
